data.title: Astonishing Biography of Joshua Mayer Aka Marshal Tito PDF
data.meta_description:
Astonishing Biography of Joshua Mayer aka Marshal Tito.pdf - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. 1) Josip Broz, born in 1892 in Croatia, died in 1914 while fighting in World War 1. His identity was later adopted by Josua Ambroz Mayer. 
2) Josua Ambroz Mayer was born in 1891 in Vienna to a Polish Jewish father and Slovenian mother. He became a communist and changed his name to Josip Broz Tito.
3) Tito led Yugoslavia's communist resistance during World War 2 and later became the lifelong president of Yugoslavia from 1953 until his death in 1980. However, he was responsible for massacring over 100,000 victims during his rule.
